<% content_for :title, "Privacy Policy" %>

<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>

  <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none">
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8">Last updated: June 2026</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">When you use Home Inspect Pro, we collect the following types of information:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
      <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Your name, email address, and password when you create an account.</li>
      <li><strong>Profile Information:</strong> Your country selection and billing information (processed securely through Paddle).</li>
      <li><strong>Inspection Data:</strong> Property addresses, client names and emails, inspection checklists, photos, comments, and digital signatures you create while using the app.</li>
      <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> How you interact with the app, including features used and inspection counts.</li>
      <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> Device type, operating system version, and app version for analytics and troubleshooting.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
      <li>To provide and maintain the inspection service</li>
      <li>To generate and deliver inspection reports to you and your clients</li>
      <li>To process subscriptions and payments (via Paddle)</li>
      <li>To send service-related communications (receipts, confirmations)</li>
      <li>To improve and optimize the app experience</li>
      <li>To provide customer support</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">3. Data Sharing</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">We do not sell your personal data. We share data only with essential service providers:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
      <li><strong>Paddle:</strong> Payment processing and subscription management</li>
      <li><strong>Cloudflare R2:</strong> File storage for uploaded photos and generated PDFs</li>
      <li><strong>Resend:</strong> Email delivery for sending reports to clients</li>
      <li><strong>Sentry:</strong> Error monitoring and crash reporting (anonymized)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">4. Data Retention</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">We retain your inspection data for as long as your account is active. If you cancel your subscription, your data is retained for 30 days before permanent deletion. You may request earlier deletion by contacting support.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">5. Your Rights</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Depending on your location, you may have the right to:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
      <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
      <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
      <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
      <li>Export your data in a portable format</li>
      <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">To exercise any of these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@homeinspectpro.app" class="text-teal-600 hover:text-teal-700">privacy@homeinspectpro.app</a>.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">6. Data Security</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">We implement industry-standard security measures including encryption in transit (TLS), encryption at rest, and regular security audits. Payment processing is handled entirely by Paddle and never touches our servers.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">7. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Home Inspect Pro uses the following third-party services. Each has its own privacy policy governing data handling:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
      <li>Paddle (payments) — <a href="https://www.paddle.com/legal/privacy" class="text-teal-600 hover:text-teal-700">paddle.com/legal/privacy</a></li>
      <li>Cloudflare (file storage) — <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" class="text-teal-600 hover:text-teal-700">cloudflare.com/privacypolicy</a></li>
      <li>Resend (email) — <a href="https://resend.com/legal/privacy-policy" class="text-teal-600 hover:text-teal-700">resend.com/legal/privacy-policy</a></li>
      <li>Sentry (error monitoring) — <a href="https://sentry.com/privacy/" class="text-teal-600 hover:text-teal-700">sentry.com/privacy</a></li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of material changes via email or in-app notification.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">9. Contact</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">For questions about this privacy policy or your data, contact us:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
      <li>Email: <a href="mailto:privacy@homeinspectpro.app" class="text-teal-600 hover:text-teal-700">privacy@homeinspectpro.app</a></li>
      <li>Support: <a href="<%= support_path %>" class="text-teal-600 hover:text-teal-700"><%= support_url %></a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>
